widget" data-widget_type=3D"text-editor.default">
				<div class=3D"elementor-widget-container">
									<p><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">Your </span><b>solar system</=
b><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;"> needs 2-5 kW of power, depending on yo=
ur home or business requirements. At </span><a href=3D"https://cosmosolaris=
.us/"><b>Cosmo Solaris</b></a><span style=3D"font-weight: 400;">, we believ=
e that understanding your energy use is the first step to making smarter ch=
oices. In this article, we will describe what a kilowatt hour (kWh) is, wha=
t a kilowatt (kW) is and how to convert from each. Once you learn this know=
ledge, we will explain how to convert from these units of measure. This is =
to give you a better understanding, but also a way to advance your home=E2=
=80=99s solar panel system.</span></p>								</div>
				</div>
				</div>
		<div class=3D"elementor-element elementor-element-2be7e2c e-con-full e-fl=
